Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:04.00,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2\fad(500,500)}翻译：绿豆  小怡       时间：小光       压制：Tanaous     后期：Salty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過武力根絕戰爭  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是天行者本色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是Gundam本色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:41.83,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私設武裝組織天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介入世界各地的紛爭之後 5年過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西曆2309年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立了地球聯邦政府的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將地球圈完全統一化了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並成立了獨立治安維持部隊A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府勢力被逐一鎮壓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後4年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在世界各地旅途奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注視著這因為天行者的武力介入而滿目瘡痍的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 這重生…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否能說是正確的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世間的扭曲 如今還慄然再目不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:03:00.06,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}拉格朗日4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年不見了啊 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中變了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你倒是一點都沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還和那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 說的真輕巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼長時間裡都幹什麼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅遊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了親眼見證這個因為我們的武力介入而變革的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依你所見 現在這世界如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由聯邦政府直轄的獨立治安維持部隊A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺那幕後一定隱藏著更加濃郁的陰霾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等也是同感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此才再次展開行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們一直在等待 你的出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還為此準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所搭乘的新機體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這來 索蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜 我選擇繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身負罪孽 沒有理由逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我領悟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥並非只有破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥中似乎也能醞釀著新生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了哦 索蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人 如此對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法停步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和世界對立起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:05:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我們無法逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是天行者的Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西曆2307年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私設武裝組織天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為根絕世界各地的紛爭展開了武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 目標瞄準狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 進入介入狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞·哈普狄斯姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 將目標 日掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞．愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 驅逐目標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那．F．塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4個機師們的戰鬥開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:06:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照斯米拉琪·李·諾莉艾卡戰況各機自行應對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你們的戰果 所以好好幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相應的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會徹底的解決掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你在聽麼 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以美國為中心的Union
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中國 俄羅斯 印度為中心的人類革新聯盟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西歐共同體AEU
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在世界各色各樣的紛爭中展開武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 我和那傢伙相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改寫我命運的那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里·阿魯·沙歇斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒想要不受一點傷就得手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然槍傷不到你 就用砍的好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個動作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光語 竟然要我從駕駛艙出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要徒手相鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼呀 特地把爺叫出來就為了這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少露個臉讓爺瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:07:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏了 偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是故意射偏的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊中的話剎那也要受牽連 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事待會再問你 任務繼續執行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳過第五階段 開始執行第六階段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 請你負責支援Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向Kyrios和Virtue也下達同樣的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞 剎那好像又做蠢事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 我沒心情說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我為什麼要揍你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam機師的身份是和太陽爐一樣 屬於S級的機密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要向敵人暴露真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想說的話就不必說了 你真是一個危險的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手提艾利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續放縱他干蠢事的話 我們也有可能被捲入危險之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的計劃才剛剛開始 如果栽在這樣的事情上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放棄駕駛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放棄駕駛Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Gundam的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下槍 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然違反了命令的我沒什麼資格說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們是由維塔選拔出來的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那他是有著被選為Gundam機師的理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 我倒想看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作為機師的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在本身就是理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的我們 且不說同伴之間友誼出現裂縫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰友意識已經開始薄弱化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至說是成是反目都不為過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們如今能如此談話 都要感激於那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今回憶起來真是覺得羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的我 一味地只知道執行計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外的東西都看得很淡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是讓我醒悟的人是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是洛克昂 他造就了我成為機師的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙比起我們更具有人性的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕 戰鬥也並非其真心所願
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他有戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要為被恐怖襲擊奪去生命的家屬報仇這種理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害洛克昂的恐怖組織KPSA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 過去我曾經隸屬於的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被強迫信仰神言的年少時代的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了給我的家人報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我的怨念得以平息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾信仰神明 被迫去信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說這不是你的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信仰神明 然後否定神明的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KPSA的頭目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里·阿魯·沙歇斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想確認他的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道他的神明在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他不再信仰神明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我…到現在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想聽一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算用Exia做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根絕戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我幹掉你就不能如願了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能代替我實現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替我校正這畸形的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我還活著 我就會戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:13:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非作為索蘭·依伯拉罕而是作為天行者的Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛著Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 太傻瓜了 我都射不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是個了不得的Gundam傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最好的稱讚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的他 代替我受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐的kiss 到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨也好 責備也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是洛克昂卻如此地關照我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備一直這樣到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是像以前那樣的傲慢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了作為機師的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不配做機師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不配…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是連接不能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就變得和我們一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔被什麼人控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有維塔的話這個計劃將…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了根除戰爭才駕駛Gundam戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候洛克昂的話 改變了我的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠實地執行伊奧利亞的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執著於根絕紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些 我選擇了和同伴們一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按自己的意識行動…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂說的是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞也如他一樣 依照自己的意識將Gundam托付給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN兵裝…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯特拉特斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 你那身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝你關心了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 現在要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人生是嘲諷的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到家族的仇人居然出現在洛克昂的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里·阿魯·沙歇斯嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里·阿魯·沙歇斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人 介入到了我們的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…居然駕駛著Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KPSA的沙歇斯吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 聽庫爾吉斯的小鬼說了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮愛爾蘭自殺恐怖襲擊的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢把無關的人也捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是同類麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行什麼戰爭根絕的恐怖主義者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不能放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這製造戰爭的源頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神氣什麼 你不也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我和你相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機接近 敵機接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}看不見!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損傷嚴重 損傷嚴重…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥不能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提 洛克昂和那個傢伙戰鬥 大概是本意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…我也不是很肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那傢伙 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是要做些不得了的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為家族報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根絕戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論哪一方面都是如此渴求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為人類 作為家人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的 躲哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幹掉這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把仇報了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不能前進啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不能面對世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活體反應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準射擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的話 可是會回不去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不到過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 這之後的明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾活著的未來就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 找到答案了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們滿意了麼 這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很討厭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了他我們有戰鬥的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂存在 那就是活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心存亡者 面對世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了神明 而是遵從自我的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他成員都怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還繼續留在天行者組織中麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩·維斯迪和菲露特·庫蕾伊絲還在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是克麗絲蒂娜·雪拉\N和裡希特達魯·歇爾利在四年前的戰鬥中犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後 斯米拉琪·李·諾莉艾卡還離開了天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·諾莉艾卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼阿雷魯亞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.36,0:21:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞·哈普狄斯姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞下落不明？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這四年中 我一直在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直… 在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考著和我同一超人機關出身的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪·皮瑞斯的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該是原本的她 瑪麗·帕法茜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 頭好…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 你離開指定路線了 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.06,0:22:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 有什麼東西… 在刺激… 我的大腦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 何方神聖 擅自闖進我的身體裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.05,0:22:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 那居然是和瑪麗在再會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.12,0:22:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.86,0:22:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和我的腦量子波相產生如此強烈的干涉的 就只有瑪麗了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我落入人革聯的陷阱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios被俘獲的時候也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.20,0:23:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 受到瑪麗的腦量子波的干擾 我失去了意識
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 他覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體中另一個我 哈雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.34,0:23:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音 聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要干擾我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那個時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人的聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 前方有部隊接近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶機翼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:24:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵人的高機動超兵型
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯了 我的腦量子波被你攪得挺慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是同類吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.68,0:24:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.27,0:24:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體各處被強化 大腦也被隨意擺弄的 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.90,0:24:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改造人體 製造完美戰士的超兵特務機關依然存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.06,0:24:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一樣 有許多被改造 被送上戰場的同胞們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.10,0:24:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提出了對超兵機關的攻擊計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.14,0:24:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為Gundam機師前往現場
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.53,0:24:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了面對自己的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.66,0:24:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也為了像我這樣的人 今後不會再出現
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.25,0:24:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個設施中有我的同類
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.83,0:25:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們並沒有罪過 有罪的是人革聯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.14,0:25:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是三大國家群
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.69,0:25:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們之間的力量角逐遊戲將世界扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.54,0:25:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誕生了我這種人體兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.62,0:25:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為了糾正這世界 我成為了Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.54,0:25:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為此我不能不痛下殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.00,0:25:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將同類們 同伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.90,0:25:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那或許是錯誤的也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.80,0:25:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 瑪麗 你的話會做出怎樣的回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.18,0:25:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣的…回答
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.71,0:25:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…好疼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.98,0:25:40.15,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}頭…好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.70,0:25:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.38,0:25:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被改造了啊 而且什麼時候要來殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.75,0:25:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向敵機示弱了麼 還是別的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.39,0:25:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要來依靠我了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.73,0:25:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避自己所厭惡的事 想說自己是無罪的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.95,0:25:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是會下手的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.75,0:26:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人的事情我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.32,0:26:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為了守護自己的存在而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.36,0:26:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.43,0:26:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你為何摻和進來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.63,0:26:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是做為天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.17,0:26:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來殺人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.92,0:26:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是作為Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.59,0:26:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要靠立場來殺人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.02,0:26:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣下扳機開火吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.54,0:26:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由真正的自己來開火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.51,0:26:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷酷無情的開火吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.66,0:26:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想開槍…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.66,0:26:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.20,0:26:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想開槍啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.52,0:26:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.35,0:27:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷魯亞也許是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.92,0:27:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪 皮瑞斯就是瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.87,0:27:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了她的存在 我就會放棄戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.80,0:27:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊阿雷魯亞 我還不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.82,0:27:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗體E57
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.45,0:27:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的說
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.13,0:27:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.65,0:27:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.64,0:27:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽的 誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.83,0:27:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長翅膀的在衛星群的什麼地方躲起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.90,0:27:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種機體狀況逃不了多遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.00,0:27:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了麼 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.12,0:27:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.97,0:27:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.72,0:27:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回裡面去 阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.35,0:27:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒你這生死線上什麼都做不到的傢伙什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.70,0:28:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.71,0:28:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要吸乾其他生者的血也會
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.02,0:28:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.44,0:28:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.47,0:28:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 還沒聽到世界的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.74,0:28:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這場戰鬥的意義也…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.40,0:28:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞭解到那些之前 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.42,0:28:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.60,0:28:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於有那種意思了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.59,0:28:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去給那女人看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.50,0:28:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的「超兵」的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.43,0:28:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.20,0:28:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直線攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.34,0:28:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避給你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.83,0:28:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕哈雷魯亞 將這力量隱藏是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.63,0:28:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用這力量的話 就會被哈雷魯亞所牽引
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.57,0:28:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪取他人生命 無法對生者救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.05,0:28:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.65,0:28:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.68,0:28:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒功夫像以前那樣慢悠悠的!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.97,0:29:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 阿雷魯亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.62,0:29:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.78,0:29:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.50,0:29:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.03,0:29:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完全不知情的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.62,0:29:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接受改造的超兵手術室中
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.18,0:29:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那過去施於那迷失的我陽光的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.23,0:29:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.58,0:29:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如字面意思 你就是瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.56,0:29:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻…要殺掉為我祈福的你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.51,0:29:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.14,0:29:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.73,0:29:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.45,0:29:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在 皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.64,0:30:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…為何
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.95,0:30:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何你…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.84,0:30:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣 索瑪·皮瑞斯就是瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.12,0:30:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道了吧 哈雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.44,0:30:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了又怎樣 你會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.13,0:30:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 怎樣都好 我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.48,0:30:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.08,0:30:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.19,0:30:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.98,0:30:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷魯亞不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.08,0:30:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被敵人監禁 他還存活在我體內
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.98,0:30:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再和她重逢之前
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.21,0:31:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拯救她之前 瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.01,0:31:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞 應該沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.39,0:31:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堅信 他 同伴還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.93,0:31:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.29,0:31:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就抵達托密勒的停留地了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.53,0:31:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的戰鬥現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.70,0:31:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和計劃無關 而是遵照我們的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.16,0:31:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.08,0:31:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我們…就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.41,0:32:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引發世界的變革 是我們的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.82,0:32:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不再度糾正這變革 則無法贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.06,0:32:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓2個太陽爐同步工作 產生平方倍的粒子量
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.68,0:32:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 00的GN system
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.99,0:32:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.60,0:32:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者的Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.82,0:32:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由自己去扣下扳機 已經連羞恥感都喪失了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.34,0:32:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使任務失敗了 我也不會蜷縮到你背後
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.34,0:32:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們 無論如何 都要救出阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.71,0:32:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種將目光游離開現實的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.36,0:32:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是無意識的惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.03,0:32:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會招致這種結果
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.78,0:32:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一能斷言的 就是戰鬥會繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.35,0:32:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼時間哭哭啼啼的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.35,0:32:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.85,0:33:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 讓這樣的我活下去 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.00,0:33:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam 剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.20,0:33:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.05,0:33:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士Gundam00 second season
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.56,0:33:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再度降臨的天使們 展開了新的任務


